26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_therm_fannil.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:35 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "priv.h"
30
31static int
32nvkm_fannil_get(struct nvkm_therm *therm)
33{
34 return -ENODEV;
35}
36
37static int
38nvkm_fannil_set(struct nvkm_therm *therm, int percent)
39{
40 return -ENODEV;
41}
42
43int
44nvkm_fannil_create(struct nvkm_therm *therm)
45{
46 struct nvkm_fan *priv;
47
48 priv = kzalloc(sizeof(*priv), GFP_KERNEL);
49 therm->fan = priv;
50 if (!priv)
51 return -ENOMEM;
52
53 priv->type = "none / external";
54 priv->get = nvkm_fannil_get;
55 priv->set = nvkm_fannil_set;
56 return 0;
57}
